        |                         porttitor leo adipiscing venenatis vehicula. Aenean quis viverra
        |                         enim. Praesent porttitor ut ipsum id ornare.
    +panel('Summernote Air-Mode')
      #summernote_air(data-plugin='summernote', data-air-mode='true')
